anov vjovanov   4096 May  5 01:48 human-intervention-logs\ndrwxrwxr-x 406 vjovanov vjovanov  20480 May  5 01:48 metadata\n-rw-rw-r--   1 vjovanov vjovanov    385 May  5 01:48 settings.gradle\ndrwxrwxr-x  11 vjovanov vjovanov   4096 May  5 01:48 skills\ndrwxrwxr-x 400 vjovanov vjovanov  20480 May  5 01:48 stats\ndrwxrwxr-x   5 vjovanov vjovanov   4096 May  5 01:48 tests\n---\nrg: logs: IO error for operation on logs: No such file or directory (os error 2)\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
